3f60de24-1815-4d88-a8dc-5ceda3f41bdc.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid
3f60de24-1815-4d88-a8dc-5ceda3f41bdc.description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid Shoe is inspired by the first AJ1, offering OG fans a look at how far the Jordan brand has come since 1985.

d52fd362-1080-46b3-a43c-d64f7a6825ab.name: Nike Air Zoom-Type
d52fd362-1080-46b3-a43c-d64f7a6825ab.description: Celebrate Nike innovation and sports heritage in the Nike Air Zoom-Type. It brings a deconstructed, DIY aesthetic to the streets with its zigzag stitching, and colors inspired by Japan's street culture. The stacked foam at the heel and contrast-colored Zoom Air cushioning at the forefoot use the same technology used by the world's elite athletes for an unparalleled ride.

891d4a42-0d8f-4f31-b201-58b3383887c8.name: Nike DBreak-Type
891d4a42-0d8f-4f31-b201-58b3383887c8.description: Deconstruct the past and step into the present with the Nike DBreak-Type. The airy mesh upper and exaggerated stitching add a bold, fresh look onto early Bowerman prototypes pulled from the archives. Retro suede and heel clips designed for support keep you connected to history while the rubber Waffle outsole features flashy angling at the back for a modern look.

23b92127-dbca-4f3e-a091-189ee55d0db1.name: Nike Air Force 1 '07
23b92127-dbca-4f3e-a091-189ee55d0db1.description: Hoops in the park, Sunday BBQs and sunshine. The radiance lives on in the Nike Air Force 1 ’07, the b-ball OG that puts a fresh spin on what you know best: crisp leather, stitched overlays in classic all-white and the perfect amount of flash to make you shine.

e4492897-c125-467b-befc-b1afba525b12.name: Nike SB Nyjah Free 2
e4492897-c125-467b-befc-b1afba525b12.description: The Nike SB Nyjah Free 2 is a sequel worthy of its predecessor. Inspired by the iconic Nike Air Zoom Spiridon, the original rubber design has been updated with mesh panels to help your feet stay cool through your hottest skate sessions.

545b44bd-31e3-490d-8b58-edb4c45f11f4.name: Nike Blazer Mid '77 Vintage
545b44bd-31e3-490d-8b58-edb4c45f11f4.description: The Nike Blazer Mid '77 Vintage harnesses the old-school look of Nike basketball with a vintage midsole finish, making it look like you've been saving them for years.

320dcd0f-a746-42b1-b6f5-c38fb33cc1c8.name: Nike Air VaporMax Plus
320dcd0f-a746-42b1-b6f5-c38fb33cc1c8.description: The Nike Air VaporMax Plus looks to the past and propels you into the future. Nodding to the 1998 Air Max Plus with its floating cage, padded upper and heel logo, it adds revolutionary VaporMax Air technology to ramp up the comfort and create a modern look.

f2a10c1b-c3fe-40b9-a5a6-395cc46a6458.name: Nike Air Max 2090
f2a10c1b-c3fe-40b9-a5a6-395cc46a6458.description: Bring the past into the future with the Nike Air Max 2090, a bold look inspired by the DNA of the iconic Air Max 90. Brand-new Nike Air cushioning underfoot adds unparalleled comfort while transparent mesh and vibrantly colored textile on select colorways blend with timeless OG features for an edgy, modernized look.

df009d76-6e99-4560-a8d7-683106d4eda3.name: Nike Air Vapormax 360
df009d76-6e99-4560-a8d7-683106d4eda3.description: Inspired by heritage running shoes like the 2006 Air Max 360, the Nike Air Vapormax 360 reimagines full-length Air with its lighter, more flexible design. The full-length foam midsole adds to the comfort while bold colors create a fresh, modern look.

29d787f5-bd0a-420a-833c-93e0812214c9.name: LeBron 17 Low
29d787f5-bd0a-420a-833c-93e0812214c9.description: Fine-tuned for LeBron's ferocious game, the LeBron 17 Low gives the King another sensation to add to his arsenal. The combined cushioning platform provides a balanced mix of impact absorption and responsiveness. A precisely crafted low-top design offers a lightweight, conforming fit with ankle mobility and a look that resonates on the street.

3b077854-50f5-478e-8ad6-58c1be611c6a.name: Nike Air VaporMax Flyknit 3
3b077854-50f5-478e-8ad6-58c1be611c6a.description: Rebel against gravity in the Nike Air VaporMax Flyknit 3. A high-fashion inspired upper features flowing lines of breathable, stretchable Flyknit construction. The revolutionary VaporMax Air technology underfoot keeps a spring in your step from toe-to-heel.

61b6247a-6210-4bd8-afe4-34bb1787bc1d.name: Nike Air Max 90 N7
61b6247a-6210-4bd8-afe4-34bb1787bc1d.description: Nothing as fly, nothing as comfortable, nothing as proven. Celebrate the proud history of Native Americans and Indigenous peoples in North America with the Nike Air Max 90 N7. Color reveal suedes let you create a 1-of-a-kind design that adds vibrancy and texture to your look while the Waffle outsole, stitched overlays and classic TPU accents stay true to its OG running roots. To finish it off, ultra-soft Nike Air cushioning adds comfort to your journey.

416d4c97-8572-490e-b95a-63eaecbac4c5.name: Kyrie 6 N7
416d4c97-8572-490e-b95a-63eaecbac4c5.description: We each have a story to tell. Distinct symbols on the Kyrie 6 N7 reflect Kyrie Irving’s personal journey and reconnection to his indigenous roots. A star representing his community is inspired by the long history of Lakota quilt design. The mountain stands for his Lakota name, Hela or Little Mountain—symbols of strength Kyrie carries with him on and off the court.

1d83991c-3a2a-43d7-b9e3-e975905fcecf.name: Kyrie 6
1d83991c-3a2a-43d7-b9e3-e975905fcecf.description: Designed for Kyrie Irving's creative and unpredictable game, the Kyrie 6 focuses on comfort, control and energy return to help him go fast and stay fresh. Bouncy cushioning is paired with soft yet supportive foam for responsiveness and smooth heel-to-toe transitions, while the midfoot strap and plush, padded collar lock him in and help keep him a step ahead of the competition.

388d6722-8abc-4c9a-bbdc-7c93f692ff22.name: KD13
388d6722-8abc-4c9a-bbdc-7c93f692ff22.description: If you want to be a complete player, you have to make an impact on both ends of the floor, from tip-off to the final buzzer. The KD13—built with a full-length Zoom Air unit stitched directly to the upper and an additional Zoom Air unit in the forefoot—provides the responsiveness and optimal energy return to help you make big-time plays all game long.

297df83a-9bf8-4960-aff2-d1c9e24f213a.name: PG 4
297df83a-9bf8-4960-aff2-d1c9e24f213a.description: Paul George is the rare high-percentage shooter who's also a coach's dream on D. Designed for his unrivaled 2-way game, the PG 4 unveils a new cushioning system that's lightweight, articulated and responsive, ideal for players like PG who go hard every play.

70a8773f-085d-494f-8e3b-7e45c8fe1bc6.name: Nike Air Zoom UNVRS FlyEase
70a8773f-085d-494f-8e3b-7e45c8fe1bc6.description: Built for all basketball players and inspired by Elena Delle Donne, the Nike Air Zoom UNVRS with FlyEase technology gives you a quick and easy way to get into your shoes and onto the court. The heel of the shoe folds down to let you slip in then a strap secures the fit.

33d0298c-f675-4cf0-9c33-29392426d970.name: Nike Air VaporMax FlyKnit 3 USA
33d0298c-f675-4cf0-9c33-29392426d970.description: The Nike Air VaporMax Flyknit 3 USA is revolutionary in more ways than one. The upper features flowing, 2-tone lines of breathable, stretchable Flyknit construction that ramps up the heat while repping the red, white and blue. Plus, VaporMax Air technology keeps spring in your step with toe-to-heel cushioning.

84d90887-7f01-421f-a0aa-0f4e27d1a4f5.name: Nike Air Max 2090 BETRUE
84d90887-7f01-421f-a0aa-0f4e27d1a4f5.description: March into the future in your Nike Air Max 2090 BETRUE, a bold new look inspired by the iconic Air Max 90. Celebrating the LGBTQIA+ community, the airy upper features translucent fabric to reveal a vibrant array of Pride colors beneath. Its asymmetrical design, decorative stitching and see-through TPU heel clip add an edgy, modernized look while super soft Nike Air cushions your journey.

3a891b03-498e-4bab-9d7f-26f4256cdbb9.name: Nike Air Trainer 3
3a891b03-498e-4bab-9d7f-26f4256cdbb9.description: The Nike Air Trainer 3 was an instant hit with its clean lines, visible Air cushioning in the heel and soft padding around the ankle. This remake combines retro colors, versatile styling options with its unique lacing system and stitched leather overlays, making it a go-to choice for off-court living.

04c867a8-2904-4144-91cc-eb7e3ebc4ab6.name: Nike React Miler
04c867a8-2904-4144-91cc-eb7e3ebc4ab6.description: The Nike React Miler gives you trusted stability for miles with athlete-informed performance. Made for dependability on your long runs, its intuitive design offers a locked-in fit and a durable feel.

ea371464-9a0d-4ec5-9026-6c32b23c71c1.name: Nike Zoom Fly 3
ea371464-9a0d-4ec5-9026-6c32b23c71c1.description: Inspired by the Vaporfly, the Nike Zoom Fly 3 gives distance runners race-day comfort and durability. The power of a carbon fiber plate keeps you in the running mile after mile.

25b9a57b-93b3-49fe-8b94-d72af46dd5f2.name: Air Jordan 3 Retro SE
25b9a57b-93b3-49fe-8b94-d72af46dd5f2.description: Go wild in the Air Jordan 3 Retro SE. Part of the "Animal Instinct" pack, it features a mix of animal-inspired materials that give fresh, new identity to the iconic shoe.

584268ab-d7df-45ce-b5be-772868ff8ff9.name: Nike Air Zoom SuperRep
584268ab-d7df-45ce-b5be-772868ff8ff9.description: The Nike Air Zoom SuperRep is designed for circuit training, HIIT, short runs and other fast-paced exercise. Zoom Air cushioning in the forefoot combines with a wide, stable heel to keep you moving and lifting comfortably.

a86007e6-88d2-4915-a11d-14c9f6083c31.name: Nike React Infinity Run Flyknit
a86007e6-88d2-4915-a11d-14c9f6083c31.description: The Nike React Infinity Run Flyknit is designed to help reduce injury and keep you on the run. More foam and improved upper details provide a secure and cushioned feel. Refreshed colors bring the bright energy to your feet while you crush your miles. Lace up and feel the potential, mile after mile.

58de8449-3d80-41a8-a8c6-b6e07112decd.name: Nike Pegasus Trail 2
58de8449-3d80-41a8-a8c6-b6e07112decd.description: Find your wings on the path less traveled. The Nike Pegasus Trail 2 delivers durability and responsiveness to runners, trail athletes and outdoor enthusiasts. Versatile enough for your everyday miles, it features an ideal fit with plush cushioning and tough traction.

cbebc1ff-2b06-4b8e-98a9-7d146c7ba805.name: Nike Juniper Trail
cbebc1ff-2b06-4b8e-98a9-7d146c7ba805.description: The Nike Juniper Trail delivers a consistent ride for your off-road runs. It's built for rocky trails, helping you stay focused on the path ahead. Tough traction mixes with a lightweight design so you can keep moving when tackling challenging terrain.

d6114fec-a067-41f7-a08d-1079e59d1973.name: Nike Joyride Run Flyknit
d6114fec-a067-41f7-a08d-1079e59d1973.description: The Nike Joyride Run Flyknit is designed to help make running feel easier and give your legs a day off. Tiny foam beads underfoot conform to your foot for cushioning that stands up to your mileage.

e51d1eae-ef5e-49d1-a896-b51beff35297.name: Nike Zoom Fly 3
e51d1eae-ef5e-49d1-a896-b51beff35297.description: Inspired by the Vaporfly, the Nike Zoom Fly 3 gives distance runners race-day comfort and durability. The power of a carbon fiber plate and responsive cushioning keeps you in the running mile after mile.

906c8dd0-e06f-4939-8562-ef45930ed691.name: Nike Joyride Dual Run
906c8dd0-e06f-4939-8562-ef45930ed691.description: The Nike Joyride Dual Run is designed to help make running feel easier and give your legs a day off. Tiny foam beads underfoot conform to your foot for cushioning that stands up to your mileage.

9115ec80-8335-4222-8af0-cf65d8d7cfbf.name: Nike Renew Run
9115ec80-8335-4222-8af0-cf65d8d7cfbf.description: The Nike Renew Run keeps you moving with softer foam for a cushioned feel. Designed with the everyday runner in mind, this shoe delivers secure support and durable traction for comfort on the go.

27054043-6a6e-4b63-8662-945794c5adc1.name: Nike React Phantom Run Flyknit 2
27054043-6a6e-4b63-8662-945794c5adc1.description: The Nike React Phantom Run Flyknit 2 is all about versatility for the everyday runner. The shoe expands on its laceless design by adding secure comfort that feels like it disappears on your foot. More foam means better cushioning, keeping you comfortable as you run.

9f257f23-9f52-4510-a485-d6e4baa410ec.name: Nike React Vision By You
9f257f23-9f52-4510-a485-d6e4baa410ec.description: Inspired by the mythical creatures of Mexican folk art, the Nike React Vision By You serves up a palette of textures, graphics and materials that let you express your wild side. Choose from 3 different mesh options that provide a natural feel and allow your foot to breathe. Add surreal comfort with Nike React foam and a personal message on the heel clip for a shoe that could only come from the dream world.

00a1dcdc-4f68-4a63-8511-41f1efc4a9a2.name: Nike Revolution 5
00a1dcdc-4f68-4a63-8511-41f1efc4a9a2.description: The Nike Revolution 5 cushions your stride with soft foam to keep you running in comfort. Lightweight knit material offers breathable support, while a minimalist design fits in anywhere your day takes you.

ef3b75d6-0017-44e1-8f36-80f0b346610b.name: Nike React Miler
ef3b75d6-0017-44e1-8f36-80f0b346610b.description: The Nike React Miler gives you trusted stability for miles with athlete-informed performance. Made for dependability on your long runs, its intuitive design offers a locked-in fit and a durable feel.

850adcdf-e894-4df8-ac81-872dedf96a34.name: Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 37
850adcdf-e894-4df8-ac81-872dedf96a34.description: Reinvigorate your stride with the Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 37. Delivering the same fit and feel that runners love, the shoe has an all-new forefoot cushioning unit and foam for maximum responsiveness. The result is a durable, lightweight trainer designed for everyday running.

96d297b2-5943-4194-be5c-f8edae4c7cf9.name: Nike Zoom Pegasus Turbo 2
96d297b2-5943-4194-be5c-f8edae4c7cf9.description: The Nike Zoom Pegasus Turbo 2 is updated with a featherlight upper, while innovative foam brings revolutionary responsiveness to your long distance training.

88e475b9-dc19-4221-86a3-18b40bb6174f.name: Nike Air Zoom Structure 22
88e475b9-dc19-4221-86a3-18b40bb6174f.description: The Nike Air Zoom Structure 22 Women's Running Shoe looks fast and feels secure. Engineered mesh, a heel overlay and dynamic support throughout the midfoot all work together to provide a smooth, stable ride.

5c691b95-fa27-48af-a32a-c1247dcc1dca.name: Nike Wildhorse 6
5c691b95-fa27-48af-a32a-c1247dcc1dca.description: The Nike Wildhorse 6 keeps it stable, secure and lightweight on the trail. An updated outsole delivers the traction you need, while a foam midsole keeps you cushioned on your run.

47e0b13d-d0d5-4fbe-b990-2b9247ddaee2.name: Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 36 Trail
47e0b13d-d0d5-4fbe-b990-2b9247ddaee2.description: An icon hits the paths less traveled in the Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 36 Trail. Perforated mesh upper offers breathable comfort, and double Zoom Air units cushion your stride. Outsole lugs optimize traction when running uphill.

6b903a5f-eec2-4a0d-90f8-75f2ea07a638.name: Nike Revolution 5 FlyEase
6b903a5f-eec2-4a0d-90f8-75f2ea07a638.description: Designed with a zip closure secured by a midfoot strap, the Nike Revolution 5 FlyEase lets you suit up for your run quickly and easily. Soft foam cushions your stride, while a minimalist design fits in just about anywhere.

e73e9417-1beb-444d-92f5-8f2ac75533bb.name: Nike Air Zoom Winflo 7
e73e9417-1beb-444d-92f5-8f2ac75533bb.description: The Nike Air Zoom Winflo 7 keeps you running with an updated mesh design and increased foam. Designed with longer runs in mind, its cushioned feel helps you stay focused on the path ahead.

de22ea4b-3824-4de6-aa90-128fb8aeba6b.name: Nike Air Zoom Vomero 14
de22ea4b-3824-4de6-aa90-128fb8aeba6b.description: The Nike Air Zoom Vomero 14 takes responsive cushioning to the next level. The full-length Zoom Air unit works with Nike React cushioning to deliver a super snappy, smooth ride. Up top, the sleek design is engineered to support your stride.

33c81e6a-4eee-43c9-b64d-907c8c4e670b.name: Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 36
33c81e6a-4eee-43c9-b64d-907c8c4e670b.description: The iconic Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 36 returns with more perforations and engineered mesh in the upper for targeted breathability across high-heat areas. A slimmer heel collar and tongue reduce bulk without compromising comfort, while exposed Flywire cables give you a snug fit at higher speeds.

ce9bf619-f99a-4a38-8f8c-fe13eba6a5e4.name: Nike Odyssey React Flyknit 2
ce9bf619-f99a-4a38-8f8c-fe13eba6a5e4.description: The Nike Odyssey React Flyknit 2 Women's Running Shoe delivers a strategic combination of lightweight Flyknit and synthetic material for support just where you need it. Underfoot, Nike React cushioning delivers a soft, springy ride for a route that begs to be crushed.

ff85be60-5675-4f81-b826-ecd92c48c274.name: Nike Zoom Pegasus Turbo
ff85be60-5675-4f81-b826-ecd92c48c274.description: The Nike Zoom Pegasus Turbo is the Pegasus you know and love with major upgrades for speed. The featherlight upper looks as fast as it feels, while the revolutionary Nike ZoomX foam that was designed for elite Nike runners during the Breaking 2 attempt brings record-breaking speed and responsiveness to your daily training runs.

ce76113e-cec9-4319-8bdd-3b28ce2d67ba.name: Nike Zoom Pegasus Turbo 2 Special Edition
ce76113e-cec9-4319-8bdd-3b28ce2d67ba.description: The Nike Zoom Pegasus Turbo 2 is updated with a featherlight upper, while energy-returning foam brings revolutionary responsiveness to your long distance training.

db07562e-653f-40d3-9564-52726d2296d9.name: Nike Zoom Gravity Icon Clash
db07562e-653f-40d3-9564-52726d2296d9.description: Designed to make fast go faster, the Nike Zoom Gravity Icon Clash is built to take you from quick tempo runs to winning races. Snappy forefoot responsiveness and grippy, multi-surface traction combine to optimize your stride.

076890ba-651c-435b-bb84-e0627b2ba76d.name: Kyrie 6
076890ba-651c-435b-bb84-e0627b2ba76d.description: Kyrie's game is serious business, but you know he's having a blast. The Kyrie 6 for little kids has all the speedy, sporty style of the shoe he wears that's made to play every day.

6d79e034-969d-4bf8-a182-98b8ca566182.name: Nike Force 1
6d79e034-969d-4bf8-a182-98b8ca566182.description: The legend lives on in the Nike Force 1, with an iconic look and plenty of cushioning for comfort with every step.

94855c9b-dc57-49a9-9895-699f71fabfd0.name: Nike Kawa
94855c9b-dc57-49a9-9895-699f71fabfd0.description: The Nike Kawa Little/Big Kids' Slide helps feet recover after play and competition with a strap that conforms to the foot, ultra-soft cushioning and a flexible outsole.

e8767797-c1cf-4352-94b9-f8c6b4229d67.name: Nike Air Max 270
e8767797-c1cf-4352-94b9-f8c6b4229d67.description: Boasting the first-ever Max Air unit created specifically for Nike Sportswear, the Nike Air Max 270 delivers an Air unit that absorbs and gives back energy with every springy step. Updated for modern comfort, it nods to the original, 1991 Air Max 180 with its exaggerated tongue top and heritage tongue logo.

5b2be448-6d72-4f52-804b-e2699e6b18a6.name: Nike MD Valiant
5b2be448-6d72-4f52-804b-e2699e6b18a6.description: These everyday kicks throw it back by mashing up details from ‘80s running shoes. Plus, the Nike MD Valiant is full of history. They're named after the car that Nike's co-founder sold shoes out of during the early days—the '64 Valiant.

14966c3e-ad39-4001-aafb-178eacb8ee92.name: Nike Air Max Plus
14966c3e-ad39-4001-aafb-178eacb8ee92.description: The Nike Air Max Plus brings little feet Max Air cushioning for all-day comfort. It keeps the original Air Max design inspiration—made just for kiddos.

40ca3087-939d-4309-8ce5-95020bd53469.name: Nike Air Max 90
40ca3087-939d-4309-8ce5-95020bd53469.description: The Nike Air Max 90 lets little ones honor their favorite team. It takes the original look to a new level with more comfort and flexibility, while keeping the classic Max Air cushioning they know and love.

757a222c-f1dc-4059-b6f6-af1b37021a41.name: LeBron 17
757a222c-f1dc-4059-b6f6-af1b37021a41.description: There's only one LeBron James, but his shoe is for everybody. The LeBron 17 for little feet is comfortable and supportive all around, with the same awesome look as the one LeBron wears.

7192de53-84cf-4a5d-aa7c-5899e84639ec.name: Nike Air Max 95
7192de53-84cf-4a5d-aa7c-5899e84639ec.description: The classic Nike Air Max 95 Little Kids' Shoe features full-length foam and a visible Max Air unit that wraps the heel for cushioned comfort and a bouncy step.

1f719d25-64cd-4e50-b8ae-63f7299307bc.name: Nike Air Max 2090
1f719d25-64cd-4e50-b8ae-63f7299307bc.description: The Nike Air Max 2090 turns up an icon—30 years after the OG Air Max 90—with even more Air. Lightweight and breathable for little walkers. A see-through design peeks into the future of Max Air.

e0679ae9-6ad8-43b6-8150-f964b0bb64c3.name: Nike Air Max 270 Extreme
e0679ae9-6ad8-43b6-8150-f964b0bb64c3.description: The Nike Air Max 270 Extreme features a slip-on design with fabric that's soft, stretchy and flexible. A Max Air unit in the heel keeps little feet cushioned and comfortable. An elastic strap provides a secure and snug fit. No laces needed.

82b08dcf-d5ee-47d3-b350-625203e32337.name: Nike Renew Run
82b08dcf-d5ee-47d3-b350-625203e32337.description: The Nike Renew Run keeps little feet moving with soft foam for a cushioned feel. Its lightweight design has breathable mesh, and a hook-and-loop strap makes it easy to take it on and off.

3ab56541-191b-46fb-ad84-d992796abc51.name: Nike Air Max 270 RT
3ab56541-191b-46fb-ad84-d992796abc51.description: The Nike Air Max 270 features Nike's biggest heel Air unit yet for a supersoft ride that feels as impossible as it looks. Colors are inspired by different periods of modern art from Bauhaus to Impressionism.

ac853307-fb3e-44da-b814-7a4568b781dc.name: Nike Sunray Adjust 5
ac853307-fb3e-44da-b814-7a4568b781dc.description: The Nike Sunray Adjust 5 is built to keep up with you in water, on land or wherever adventure takes you. The quick-dry design has a strap on top and behind your heel to keep it from slipping off. Lightweight, flexible foam provides durable cushioning that lasts.

9ed46dd5-c448-43f6-87b0-b6fec40a6fc8.name: Nike Force 1 Mid
9ed46dd5-c448-43f6-87b0-b6fec40a6fc8.description: The Nike Force 1 Mid puts the next generation of athletes in a style that goes back years. Its classic, clean upper design sits on top of full-length cushioning for all-day comfort.

2d3de68a-efe9-464a-abe6-414d9d7bdcf6.name: Nike Pegasus '92 Lite
2d3de68a-efe9-464a-abe6-414d9d7bdcf6.description: A blast from the past! The Nike Pegasus ’92 Lite brings back an early ‘90s fave. These shoes have Pegasus swag and are comfy and durable for early walkers. Elastic laces and pull tabs help to easily slip on and off.

c6b27d84-8fad-4ec3-ae4e-2dea07946756.name: Nike Court Borough Mid 2
c6b27d84-8fad-4ec3-ae4e-2dea07946756.description: Your little one will feel like an all-star off the court with the Nike Court Borough Mid 2. The classic high-top design features durable leather for a premium look and feel. A hook-and-loop strap makes it easy to take the shoe on and off.

092f9df5-e689-4f90-b663-654ce6f39621.name: Nike Force 1 LV8 3
092f9df5-e689-4f90-b663-654ce6f39621.description: Do a double take and double the fun with the Nike Air Force 1 LV8 3. Repeat “Air” logos on the heel bring a new look while still keeping the classic feel of the ’82 original remade for kiddos.

a72b9839-1b05-40a0-ab38-eea3f147a2c7.name: Nike Air Max Excee
a72b9839-1b05-40a0-ab38-eea3f147a2c7.description: The Nike Air Max Excee honors 30 years since the release of the iconic Air Max 90. Inspired by the original design, these low-top kicks for kiddos add a crafty look and a mix of textures for a new twist on a ‘90s favorite. FYI, Excee means 90 in Latin.

768385da-e8bb-454d-97a9-658967d655dc.name: Nike RT Presto MC
768385da-e8bb-454d-97a9-658967d655dc.description: The Nike RT Presto MC has a slip-on design that feels snug and is easy to take on and off. Soft foam cushioning and lightweight fabric provide all-day comfort. The melted crayon print crafts a fun look for your feet.

86a015ea-1470-4df4-9e81-79ccee41c16d.name: Team Hustle D 9
86a015ea-1470-4df4-9e81-79ccee41c16d.description: Hustle's in the name, comfort is the game of the Nike Team Hustle D 9. Fabric lets little feet breathe and a rubber sole flexes with their foot as they learn the movements from pivots to cuts to jump stops.

5687d58e-950d-4996-8ce2-4b5bab7d1508.name: Nike Air Max Axis
5687d58e-950d-4996-8ce2-4b5bab7d1508.description: A nod to '90s running, Nike Air Max Axis for little feet honors the past while looking ahead to the future. Subtle design lines and branding pay homage to icons like the Air Max 97 and Air Max 98, while a new look at the Max Air unit offers a fresh take on cushioned comfort.

44ed0064-cc7e-44a7-8aca-89743d9ff5dd.name: Nike Air Max2 Light
44ed0064-cc7e-44a7-8aca-89743d9ff5dd.description: The Nike Air Max2 Light brings back an OG ‘90s classic for your little one. Leather and a Max Air unit combine to support growing feet in these low-top kicks. Woven laces make for easy on and off.

f2a17dc9-0305-487a-804f-c70f15a6c3cb.name: KD Trey 5 VIII
f2a17dc9-0305-487a-804f-c70f15a6c3cb.description: The KD Trey 5 VIII gives your kiddo the look and feel of one of the game’s elite players. Breathable and supportive features make it easy for your little baller to make moves like Kevin Durant at playtime.
